Breast Cancer in the Elderly.

Varghese F(1), Wong J(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Surgery, University of California, San Francisco, 1600 
Divisadero Street, Second Floor, Box 1710, San Francisco, CA 94115, USA.
(2)Department of Surgery, University of California, San Francisco, 1600 
