Crosscultural adaptation and validation into Spanish of the questionnaire 
National Eye Institute Visual Function Questionnaire 25.

[Article in English, Spanish]

Alvarez-Peregrina C(1), Sánchez-Tena MA(2), Caballé-Fontanet D(1), 
